  "instructions": [
    "In a large pan, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cumin and smoked paprika and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chickpeas and cook until heated through, about 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in the lemon juice, water, and pomegranate molasses.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the semolina flour and a pinch of salt.",
    "Gradually add the flour mixture to the chickpea mixture and stir until smooth.",
    "Add the chopped parsley, cilantro, and dill and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving dish and flatten the top slightly.",
    "Drizzle with olive oil and sprinkle with sesame seeds and chopped fresh herbs.",
    "Serve warm or at room temperature, garnished with additional chopped fresh herbs if desired."
  ],
